{"tid":1795784,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有冇得買 Sapporo 啤酒黑標？","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T09:18:10.000Z","uid":123335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6b2b8317352875a3e389701c0dbd7ff3189ea3","tid":1795784,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://beauty-upgrade.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/33-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeauty-upgrade.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F33-1.jpg&h=80ffa2b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上圖呢一款<br />\n真心覺得好飲 <br />\n大麥味岩岩好，唔會好似嘉士伯咁，太過Over <br />\ncitrus 味、啤酒花既味道亦飲得出，作為輔助性，<br />\n唔會好似1664 or 手工啤咁喧賓奪主，唔會遮蓋晒d 大麥味，留有大麥粗獷、野性既味道 <br />\n在其位，謀其事。知道自己既身份，唔會踩過界 <br />\n<br />\n香港7仔、超市買到果罐 sapporo premium beer 產地係越南 <br />\n難飲到仆街，淡而無味，650ml 版本果隻，7仔仲要賣 $30 真係on撚鳩 <br />\n日本仔真係好野就益自己友，出口就整埋d 垃圾賣俾人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下<br />\n隨左去日本旅行之外 <br />\n仲有咩途徑飲到 sapporo 黑標啤酒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc3db8ea809c21caed462bcc7cd3e7b42465d86","tid":1795784,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"bill gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcb258cd68d5fa212410b4e66d742231fea98b9","tid":1795784,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"DONK